==English==

===Adjective===
'''bendy'''
# Having the ability to be easily [[bent]].
#:''Bendy rulers are far more fun than the wooden ones.''
# [[Flexible]], having the ability to [[bend]] easily.
#:''Gymnasts are very bendy people.''
# [[windy|Windy]], having many [[bend]]s and [[twist]]s in.
#:''A bendy road''
# [[articulated|Articulated]].
#:A "[[bendy bus]]" (an [[articulated bus]]).

